description:
These videos are from the FREE and comprehensive course available at GMAT Prep Now

Data sufficiency questions account for approximately 40% of all question in the quantitative section of the GMAT. In this course, you'll learn everything you need to know to confidently tackle this complex question type. In fact, you may come to find that data sufficiency questions are actually easier than problem solving questions.
title: GMAT Data Sufficiency Strategies
